<h3 id="the-reftoken-pre-sale-and-ico">The RefToken pre-sale and ICO</h3>

<p>RefToken picked a date for their presale following the deployment of a demo. It is live and out there at <a href="https://demo.reftoken.com/">https://demo.reftoken.com/</a>.</p>

<p>The token presale was supposed to start at some point in September but actually started on October 2nd 2017. And who‚Äôs talking about it? Nobody on Reddit I‚Äôm sure. The market is flooded with token sales and ICOs by now and RefToken didn‚Äôt get anything near the attention of BAT, despite the similar niche and a glaring gap in the market.</p>

