<p>The pre-sale started on <strong>October 2nd 2017</strong> and is set to end on <strong>October 17th</strong>. Target is at 4300 ETH.</p>

<p>The total funding target is ‚Ç¨27.7M - yes it‚Äôs in EUR. If you‚Äôre a whale you can also invest in fiat, they are an <a href="https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/reftoken">actual business</a> based in <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=reftoken%20address&amp;cad=h">Malta</a>, otherwise it‚Äôs either BTC or ETH.</p>

